Compile Instructions
----------------------------------------
Make sure all files and references to said files are in (and named as) specific folders/directories (ex: helper_functions/...)

Navigate to project directory: ~/a2
by running: 
		cd a2
Then run:
		make

This will genereate the exe. files "xle" and "test"

